name: RUNNER
description: Maestro, Unibot and Banana sniper bots are known to snipe within 6 to 15 seconds depending on blockchain traffic and server issues, while Runner Sniper Bot allows sniping within 2 seconds. Where other Sniper Bots have limited wallets to snipe with, we have no limitations. We will have multisell and bundling on block 0 implemented into our sniper bot very soon!
